{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CORS","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CORS","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CORS</strong>（跨來源資源共享）是瀏覽器技術規範，用來傳輸 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers\">HTTP 標頭</a>，判斷阻擋或允許不同來源網域的資源存取。</p>\n<p><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Security/Same-origin_policy\">同源安全政策（same-origin security policy）</a>，預設會禁止跨網域的資源請求。CORS 賦予網站伺服器跨網域存取控制能力，使其能安全地跨網域傳輸資料。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"一般知識","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>MDN 上的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTTP/CORS\">HTTP 存取控制（CORS）</a></li>\n  <li>維基百科上的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cross-origin_resource_sharing\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Cross-origin resource sharing</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cors_標頭","title":"CORS 標頭","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"access-control-allow-origin\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Allow-Origin\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示回傳資料能否共享（布林值）。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"access-control-allow-credentials\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Allow-Credentials\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Access-Control-Allow-Credentials (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>指定為 <code>true</code> 時，瀏覽器可以傳送或接收敏感資訊（HTTP Cookie）。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"access-control-allow-headers\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Allow-Headers\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Access-Control-Allow-Headers (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>指定可以出現在真實請求的 HTTP 標頭，用來回應預檢請求。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"access-control-allow-methods\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Allow-Methods\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Access-Control-Allow-Methods (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>指定存取資源所允許的 HTTP 方法，用來回應預檢請求。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"access-control-expose-headers\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Expose-Headers\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Access-Control-Expose-Headers (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示瀏覽器允許存取的標頭白名單，例如 <code>X-My-Header, X-My-Custom-Header</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"access-control-max-age\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Max-Age\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Access-Control-Max-Age (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示預檢請求的回傳結果可以被快取多久（秒）。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"access-control-request-headers\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Request-Headers\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Access-Control-Request-Headers (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>用於預檢請求，讓伺服器知道後續真實請求夾帶的 HTTP 標頭。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"access-control-request-method\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Request-Method\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Access-Control-Request-Method (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>用於預檢請求，讓伺服器端知道後續真實請求使用的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTTP/Methods\">HTTP 方法</a>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"origin\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Origin\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Origin (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>告訴伺服器請求來源之網域。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術參考","title":"技術參考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Fetch specification</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"CORS（跨來源資源共享）是瀏覽器技術規範，用來傳輸 HTTP 標頭，判斷阻擋或允許不同來源網域的資源存取。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CORS","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CORS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CORS","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CORS","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"CORS","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CORS","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CORS","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/cors","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/cors/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CORS","title":"CORS"}],"pageTitle":"CORS - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}